name 'pl-java-conditionals-chk-und-boolean-3_pl'
title 'Check for understanding'
description 'For each of the statements below, assume that the **variable `num` has been declared and initialized to the value 15**.  Match the boolean expression to the correct boolean value.'
height '90'
question '`num * 2 == num + 15`'
answer '`true`'

question '`num / 5 = 2`'
answer '`false`'

allow_multiple_attempts true